---
title: Banoffee Pudding Cups Serves 4 | with DIY Toffee Sauce
description: A winning combination of DIY banana pudding, salted toffee sauce and buttery graham crumble, these pudding cups are a fun take on the classic banoffee pie!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/banoffee-pudding-cups-49283fdd.jpg
